pan style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">s and it has lost sight of its core values and responsibilities.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">It has shown scenes of violence, sex and bad language which are not necessary and which have upset many people and been available to young people.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">It has also been subject to claims of bias</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">ed reporting.  I understand that this is a subjective matter on which many people will disagree.  I believe it has consistently been pro-PLA in its reporting of the situation </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">in the Middle East as opposed to reporting the Israeli position in equal terms. </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> </span></p><ul type="disc" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:10pt; margin:5pt 0pt 6pt 23.8pt; padding-left:8.4pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">The Trust should be entirely independent of the BBC and receive its own funding.</span></li><li style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:10pt; margin:5pt 0pt 6pt 23.8pt; padding-left:8.4pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">The Trust be outward looking and include a member who represents the interests of the licence fee payer, possibly a representative from an in